Given an input CSV file adhering to following format: debtorAccount,creditoAccount,amount,date
matching Payment class, implement PaymentRepository.
Please keep in mind that any IO operation is expensive and should be invoked * as little as possible.
Introduce any data structures that will optimize method usage.
Adhere to coding principles and good practices.
Convert PaymentRepository implementation into Spring bean that could be used
in web environment so it can be safely accessed by web controllers.
Write tests (junit or testng) proving that the service works as expected.


